          BUT INSTEAD,
         YOU SNUBBED US

10:04.705 --> 10:06.771
       AND MADE ANDY JUMP
      OUT OF A MOVING CAR.

10:06.773 --> 10:09.874
       HE OPENED THE DOOR
         AND FLEW OUT!

10:09.876 --> 10:11.610
        - YOU KNOW WHAT?
JUST GET OUT OF MY HOUSE, OKAY?

10:11.612 --> 10:13.311
