11:07.734 --> 11:08.867
      BECAUSE HE'D ALREADY
           GONE OUT.

11:08.869 --> 11:10.168
           ALL WE DID
    WAS TALK ABOUT THE KIDS.

11:10.170 --> 11:11.236
       THAT'S ALL WE DID.

11:11.238 --> 11:15.173
     - IS THAT ALL YOU DID,
