11:35.095 --> 11:36.361
           ONE HOUR.

11:36.363 --> 11:38.263
        - IT'S NOT JUST
    ABOUT LAST NIGHT, ANDY.

11:38.265 --> 11:40.732
      YOU NEVER HAVE TIME
        FOR ME ANYMORE.

11:40.734 --> 11:42.467
     I MEAN, WE'VE WATCHED
   THE SUPER BOWL EVERY YEAR

11:42.469 --> 11:44.002
       SINCE HIGH SCHOOL,

11:44.004 --> 11:47.138
  AND LAST YEAR, I GOT TICKETS
       TO THE SUPER BOWL,

11:47.140 --> 11:49.174
