12:05.024 --> 12:07.358
    - OH! THAT'S DISGUSTING.

12:07.360 --> 12:08.393
       - THAT'S MY LIFE.

12:08.395 --> 12:10.195
           ALL RIGHT?
     AND THE FACT THAT YOU

12:10.197 --> 12:11.930
          CONSISTENTLY
     DON'T RECOGNIZE THAT--

12:11.932 --> 12:15.166
