    LIKE, A TEAM TO GO POOP.

12:29.015 --> 12:30.215
       - I'M SORRY, WILL.

12:30.217 --> 12:31.983
   THIS IS WHO THEY ARE NOW.

12:31.985 --> 12:33.818
     THIS IS WHO I AM NOW.

12:33.820 --> 12:35.787
   YOU MAY BE MY BEST FRIEND,

12:35.789 --> 12:38.456
     BUT YOU HAVE NOT BEEN
