13:22.235 --> 13:23.835
   AND I AM FREE TO DO THEM.

13:23.837 --> 13:26.204
       BUT DON'T BLAME ME
       FOR YOUR FREEDOM,

13:26.206 --> 13:27.305
     WHICH YOU DON'T HAVE,

13:27.307 --> 13:30.108
       OR FOR NOT BONDING
       WITH YOUR INFANTS,

13:30.110 --> 13:33.912
