14:06.046 --> 14:08.112
   I AM HERE TO BE A FRIEND.

14:08.114 --> 14:10.949
    I WOULD LIKE TO BABYSIT

14:10.951 --> 14:13.151
       THE LITTLE PEOPLE
      WHILE YOU TWO GO OUT

14:13.153 --> 14:15.920
   AND SPEND SOME ALONE TIME
