14:17.991 --> 14:20.158
  A LITTLE LESS WOULD BE IDEAL
            FOR ME.

14:20.160 --> 14:24.128
         UM, AND MAYBE
    I'LL EVEN BOND WITH, UM,

14:24.130 --> 14:27.065
       LITTLE JONAH AND--

14:27.067 --> 14:28.933
       AND THE GIRL AND--

14:28.935 --> 14:30.168
       - MADDIE AND ALEX.

14:30.170 --> 14:31.102
       - I'M GONNA LEARN
          THEIR NAMES.

14:31.104 --> 14:32.370
    - THAT--THIS IS AWESOME.

14:32.372 --> 14:33.471
        THIS IS AMAZING.

14:33.473 --> 14:35.974
    THANK YOU SO MUCH, WILL.
              SEE?

14:35.976 --> 14:37.642
     - UM, ARE YOU INSANE?

14:37.644 --> 14:40.278
       WE ARE NOT LEAVING
   OUR BABIES ALONE WITH HIM.

14:40.280 --> 14:41.346
    - CAN WE TALK ABOUT IT?

14:41.348 --> 14:44.115
  - I THINK THERE IS SOMETHING
         TO TALK ABOUT.

14:44.117 --> 14:45.550
         - [whispering]
