14:45.552 --> 14:47.418
   - LAURIE, FAMILY MEETING.

14:47.420 --> 14:48.453
              NOW.

14:48.455 --> 14:50.054
           - [gasps]

14:50.056 --> 14:51.055
    I HATE WHEN YOU DO THAT.

14:51.057 --> 14:52.624
        - JUST LET'S GO.

14:52.626 --> 14:54.192
      WE'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

14:54.194 --> 14:56.394
            COME ON.
