14:58.097 --> 15:00.365
          - [chomping]
       - FRIDGE MONSTER!

15:00.367 --> 15:02.500
        OKAY, IT'S BACK
         IN THE FRIDGE.

15:02.502 --> 15:04.235
            crunch!
              AH!

15:04.237 --> 15:05.270
             DUDE!

15:05.272 --> 15:07.505
       SECURITY DEPOSIT.

15:07.507 --> 15:08.973
            - OKAY.

15:08.975 --> 15:10.975
             SO...
   DID A LITTLE NEGOTIATING--

15:10.977 --> 15:12.110
       - HEY, BY THE WAY,
     THAT WHISPERING THING

15:12.112 --> 15:13.211
        WAS TERRIFYING.

15:13.213 --> 15:14.379
       - YEAH, ALL RIGHT.
           WHATEVER.

15:14.381 --> 15:16.214
  SO LAURIE'S NOT GONNA LEAVE
           THE HOUSE

15:16.216 --> 15:19.183
   BUT YOU CAN WATCH THE KIDS
           DOWNSTAIRS

15:19.185 --> 15:22.153
         WHILE WE SPEND
