16:02.062 --> 16:04.228
          - [laughing]
              OH.

16:04.230 --> 16:06.497
    IT'S IN THE BIBLE, WILL.

16:06.499 --> 16:09.334
         THE BABY JESUS
   IN HIS SWADDLING CLOTHES.

16:09.336 --> 16:10.401
        - OKAY, COME ON,
       COME ON, COME ON.

16:10.403 --> 16:12.103
       - I'M NOT SO SURE.
          - LET'S GO.

16:12.105 --> 16:13.471
    WE'LL BE RIGHT UPSTAIRS
      IF ANYTHING HAPPENS.

16:13.473 --> 16:16.107
 - OKAY, HEY, KIDDOS, HAVE FUN.
        USE PROTECTION.

16:16.109 --> 16:18.676
     - THE SECOND I LEAVE,
  JONAH'S GONNA START TO WAIL,

16:18.678 --> 16:20.211
     BUT HE WILL CALM DOWN
         AT SOME POINT.

16:20.213 --> 16:22.180
         COME GET ANDY
    IF MADISON HAS TO POOP,

16:22.182 --> 16:23.414
    BECAUSE SHE WON'T DO IT
          WITHOUT HIM.

16:23.416 --> 16:25.750
       - COME ON, HONEY.
   - OH, AND ALEX IS A BITER!

16:25.752 --> 16:27.285
      - WHICH ONE'S ALEX?

16:27.287 --> 16:28.619
           - [crying]
             - OW!

16:28.621 --> 16:29.754
           FOUND HIM.

16:29.756 --> 16:33.691
          - [wailing]

16:41.300 --> 16:41.532
               .

