  SHALL WE BEGIN THE BONDAGE?
        A-AS IN BONDING?

16:47.741 --> 16:49.007
        NOT BOND--NOT--

16:49.009 --> 16:51.209
          - [fussing]
          - MOVING ON.

16:51.211 --> 16:53.211
         YOU'RE JONAH,
    'CAUSE YOU'RE THE BABY.

16:53.213 --> 16:55.179
      LISTEN, I UNDERSTAND
        YOU DON'T TALK,

16:55.181 --> 16:56.280
  BUT THIS WHOLE CRYING THING
           IS JUST--

16:56.282 --> 16:57.648
