16:57.650 --> 16:59.684
   SO IF YOU COULD JUST SMILE
             OR HUM

16:59.686 --> 17:02.120
   IF YOU HAVE ANY CONCERNS,
        APPRECIATE THAT.

17:02.122 --> 17:05.256
      - OKAY, YOU'RE ALEX,
'CAUSE YOU WENT ALL <i> JAWS</i> ON ME,

17:05.258 --> 17:08.358
  WHICH I CAN'T EVEN TELL YOU
      HOW UNCOOL THAT IS.

17:08.361 --> 17:11.729
   I MEAN, WHO BITES SOMEONE
          ON THE BUTT?

17:11.731 --> 17:16.099
