17:31.117 --> 17:33.251
       NO WATER WEAPONRY
          ON MY WATCH!

17:33.253 --> 17:35.787
           - [crying]
           - OH, NO.

17:35.789 --> 17:39.257
      I THOUGHT WE TALKED
