17:39.259 --> 17:41.225
     OOH, I'M A SILLY MAN.

17:41.227 --> 17:42.460
           SILLY MAN,
           SILLY MAN.

17:42.462 --> 17:44.762
           [chuckles]

17:44.764 --> 17:47.565
         YOU KNOW WHAT?
    THIS IS JUST--WHATEVER.

17:47.567 --> 17:49.634
        - [stops crying]

17:51.103 --> 17:52.437
         - BULL'S-EYE.

17:52.439 --> 17:54.172
         - OH, MY GOD.

17:54.174 --> 17:55.273
      IT'S BEEN TOO LONG.

17:55.275 --> 17:56.541
        - WAY TOO LONG.

17:56.543 --> 17:57.542
          - LET'S GO.
