   - UH, WELL, THAT'S KIND OF
  HOW THIS WHOLE THING WORKS.

19:18.458 --> 19:19.824
   MAYBE I'LL STAND OUT HERE,

19:19.826 --> 19:21.292
          AND THEN YOU
       CAN DO YOUR THING?

19:21.294 --> 19:25.163
       - I WANT MY DADDY.

19:25.165 --> 19:27.765
          - OH, OKAY.
       OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

19:27.767 --> 19:29.834
       I'M HERE WITH YOU.
  I'M HERE WITH YOU, MADISON.

19:29.836 --> 19:31.636
           ALL RIGHT?
           IT'S OKAY.

19:31.638 --> 19:34.172
     AND THERE'S NO REASON
         TO BE SCARED.

