      - SOMETIMES MY DADDY
         HOLDS MY HAND,

19:35.842 --> 19:37.642
     WHICH SOMETIMES HELPS.

19:37.644 --> 19:40.811
  - OH, I'M--I'M GENERALLY NOT
         A HAND HOLDER.

19:40.813 --> 19:44.482
              I--

19:44.484 --> 19:46.751
  - SOMETIMES MY DADDY SINGS.

19:46.753 --> 19:48.286
          THAT HELPS.

19:48.288 --> 19:50.955
       WHAT KIND OF MUSIC
         ARE YOU INTO?

19:50.957 --> 19:52.256
       YOU LIKE HIP-HOP?

19:52.258 --> 19:53.691
       YOU LIKE COUNTRY?

19:53.693 --> 19:56.260
   YOU LIKE HAIR BAND STUFF?

19:56.262 --> 19:57.528
    -<i> POP! GOES THE WEASEL.</i>

19:57.530 --> 20:00.531
  - OH, THAT'S A GOOD CHOICE.

20:00.533 --> 20:01.699
        [clears throat]

20:01.701 --> 20:03.868
             YEAH.
           [inhales]

