           - [gasps]

20:21.321 --> 20:23.387
           I DID IT!

20:23.389 --> 20:24.889
          - [laughing]

20:24.891 --> 20:27.258
      - I LOVE YOU, WILL.

20:27.260 --> 20:28.226
          - [laughing]
             I L--

20:28.228 --> 20:30.228
    I LOVE YOU TOO, MADISON.

20:30.230 --> 20:31.596
         - OH, MY GOD.

20:31.598 --> 20:34.599
         [tender music]

20:34.601 --> 20:37.802
              ¶ ¶

20:37.804 --> 20:40.571
          THANKS, MAN.

20:40.573 --> 20:44.442
    - CAN YOU WIPE ME, WILL?
   - OKAY, YOUR DADDY'S HERE.

20:46.279 --> 20:49.280
         - "SO I CAN BE
  A BETTER GODPARENT TO YOU."

20:49.282 --> 20:50.381
      I'M NOT SAYING THIS.
        THIS IS STUPID.

20:50.383 --> 20:52.283
           - SAY IT.
    - I'M NOT GONNA SAY IT.

20:52.285 --> 20:53.317
           - SAY IT!
           - COME ON.

20:53.319 --> 20:54.986
          - "AND I VOW
       TO ALWAYS LOVE YOU

20:54.988 --> 20:57.955
    AS IF YOU WERE THE FRUIT
       OF MY OWN LOINS."

20:57.957 --> 21:00.024
       - IT'S BEAUTIFUL.
         - IT IS SICK.

21:00.026 --> 21:01.792
           I'M DONE.
            - WHAT?

21:01.794 --> 21:02.960
       - I'M OUTTA HERE.
     - WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

21:02.962 --> 21:04.695
           SERIOUSLY?

21:04.697 --> 21:06.764
         - OH, THAT'S--
      OKAY, THAT'S RIGHT.

21:06.766 --> 21:08.966
      YOU JUST GO BACK ON
        OVER THE BRIDGE!

21:08.968 --> 21:09.967
          CITY TRASH!

21:09.969 --> 21:11.769
           - [crying]
         - REAL CLASSY!

21:11.771 --> 21:12.870
      YOU DID THIS, WILL!

